<plot>Through the window of Chinese propaganda in Tibet, this film looks closely at education, entertainment, urban development, religion, political anniversary celebration, and the peaceful liberation of Tibet. The film artfully illuminates these topics by delving directly into the propaganda world, and includes interviews with five Tibetans for whom that world was a part of daily life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?152206</url></doc>
